			<div class="content" id="post-content-4230749">
									

<p>This is a nice compilation. I know you said you did this all manually and such, but I’m just going to point out that the article/SCP counts for End of Death and Apotheosis aren’t taking into account the stuff that was written after doomcon. (To some degree this is true for Lethe as well but whether or not AAPA really counts as being part of that scenario or if it’s more of its own beast building from it is your call). Both of them have their own tags since their also canons now, so it probably won’t be too hard to get the exact counts.</p>
<p>I’m also very curious where you found that alternative title for end of death, because I don’t think I’ve seen it before!</p>
<p>But yeah, good stuff!</p>

