<p>I've made this into a <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/k-class-complete-list">collaborative page</a>. If you or anyone else interested could link the EOD and Apotheosis articles there, that would make my life easier. :)</p>
<p>Edit: When I was copying from the contest hub, I included everything by the team whether or not it mentioned the scenario specifically, so adding all tagged stuff makes sense to me.</p>
<p>Crowning of Death only appeared in <a href="/scp-4260">SCP-4260</a>, which was also an Omega-K article. I wasn't sure how the two were related at the time, but the author has since informed me that χK exists exclusively from End of Death.</p>

